1
00:00:22,620 --> 00:00:26,000
♪The blood within me ignites
with a fierce desire♪

2
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,300
♪Exposing the lies
that fate has written♪

3
00:00:29,300 --> 00:00:30,760
♪No more hiding♪

4
00:00:30,760 --> 00:00:33,860
♪My martial soul has awakened
in its full strength♪

5
00:00:35,570 --> 00:00:38,760
♪Even countless of trials can't stop me♪

6
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:42,050
♪The searing heat
that surges within my chest♪

7
00:00:42,050 --> 00:00:43,440
♪I want the world♪

8
00:00:43,440 --> 00:00:47,220
♪To remember me♪

9
00:00:48,090 --> 00:00:51,930
♪Yes or no, right or wrong♪

10
00:00:51,930 --> 00:00:53,640
♪To defeat or to be defeated♪

11
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:56,940
♪Giving my all with no regrets♪

12
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,880
♪Breaking through the encirclement♪

13
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:02,030
♪It doesn't matter who my opponent is♪

14
00:01:02,030 --> 00:01:05,230
♪To shine as the new star
of Douluo Continent♪

15
00:01:05,230 --> 00:01:06,630
♪The fleeting dream of life is
easily shattered♪

16
00:01:06,630 --> 00:01:10,020
♪So why not face it boldly,
just this once♪

17
00:01:10,020 --> 00:01:11,660
♪Fierce storms and raging thunder♪

18
00:01:11,660 --> 00:01:14,880
♪Burn me, yet refine my determination♪

19
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:18,500
♪No matter how battered,
I smile and refuse to retreat♪

20
00:01:18,500 --> 00:01:22,170
♪A so-called hero, covered in dust♪

21
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,990
♪Scarred and worn♪

22
00:01:24,990 --> 00:01:26,980
♪Can still sever the cycle of fate♪

23
00:01:26,980 --> 00:01:28,320
=The Land of Warriors=

24
00:01:28,321 --> 00:01:29,980
(Adapted from
Tangjia Sanshao's novel "Soul Land")

25
00:01:30,380 --> 00:01:34,220
=Episode 16=

26
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:36,890
I'm so pitiful!

27
00:01:41,220 --> 00:01:41,890
Stop right there!

28
00:01:43,530 --> 00:01:46,090
How could an ordinary woman
possess such extreme strength?

29
00:01:47,500 --> 00:01:48,780
Who exactly are you?

30
00:01:50,020 --> 00:01:50,890
How dare you?

31
00:01:55,616 --> 00:01:58,384
Fatty said plenty of soul masters
were undergoing their training here.

32
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,600
Why didn't we see a single one

33
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,448
on our way here?

34
00:02:01,140 --> 00:02:01,730
Look.

35
00:02:03,580 --> 00:02:04,500
Look at the tracks.

36
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:07,424
These should be tracks left behind
by the armor-transporting carriage.

37
00:02:11,100 --> 00:02:11,930
Is this a trap?

38
00:02:13,024 --> 00:02:14,688
I speculate that this Martial Soul Hall

39
00:02:14,736 --> 00:02:16,020
is an empty shell by now.

40
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:17,650
Let's see what we can find.

41
00:02:26,820 --> 00:02:27,890
This must be Fatty's doing.

42
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:32,656
Someone cleaned up the place before.

43
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:34,256
Judging from the remnants,

44
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:35,860
the fire didn't burn everything down.

45
00:02:36,450 --> 00:02:37,980
Could it be that they left cautiously

46
00:02:37,980 --> 00:02:39,232
upon detecting Fatty's presence?

47
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,056
They didn't search
for Fatty in the city.

48
00:02:41,072 --> 00:02:42,816
However, they emptied
the Martial Soul Hall.

49
00:02:43,210 --> 00:02:44,050
This makes no sense.

50
00:02:44,336 --> 00:02:46,260
I suppose they had no time
to care about Fatty.

51
00:02:52,128 --> 00:02:53,712
Let's rendezvous with Fatty.

52
00:02:53,728 --> 00:02:55,550
Let's report this to Father
tomorrow morning.

53
00:03:02,330 --> 00:03:03,210
That hurts.

54
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:04,020
Fatty?

55
00:03:04,050 --> 00:03:04,700
That hurts!

56
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:06,860
Hurry and get up.

57
00:03:08,580 --> 00:03:09,050
Fatty,

58
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,450
did someone take advantage of you?

59
00:03:10,770 --> 00:03:13,100
I was buying time
for you guys, you know?

60
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:15,700
The scums at the entrance
are so annoying.

61
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,330
Why are you standing here?

62
00:03:17,330 --> 00:03:18,050
Time to run.

63
00:03:18,050 --> 00:03:18,650
They're coming.

64
00:03:18,656 --> 00:03:19,056
Let's go.

65
00:03:19,300 --> 00:03:19,700
Let's go.

66
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:22,580
Fatty, you look pretty good
in a woman's attire.

67
00:03:22,650 --> 00:03:23,380
Shut up!

68
00:03:36,490 --> 00:03:37,300
Tang Long,

69
00:03:37,650 --> 00:03:38,980
invite the two elders here again.

70
00:03:39,050 --> 00:03:39,610
Yes, sir.

71
00:03:40,020 --> 00:03:40,890
No need for that.

72
00:03:43,490 --> 00:03:44,420
We're here.

73
00:03:51,450 --> 00:03:52,020
Tang San,

74
00:03:52,610 --> 00:03:53,700
greet the two elders.

75
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:56,490
I...

76
00:03:57,210 --> 00:03:58,020
Chief.

77
00:03:58,496 --> 00:03:59,860
(Seventh Elder of Haotian Sect)

78
00:03:59,860 --> 00:04:02,050
Why did you allow an outsider
to enter Haotian Sect?

79
00:04:02,330 --> 00:04:03,380
Is Haotian Sect

80
00:04:03,490 --> 00:04:05,140
available for all kinds of people now?

81
00:04:05,900 --> 00:04:08,540
(Second Elder of Haotian Sect)

82
00:04:08,930 --> 00:04:11,450
San inherited the bloodline
and martial soul of Haotian Sect.

83
00:04:11,730 --> 00:04:12,610
He's not an outsider.

84
00:04:12,992 --> 00:04:14,540
(Tang Hu, Disciple of Haotian Sect)

85
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:15,140
Chief,

86
00:04:15,700 --> 00:04:16,850
the son of a sinner

87
00:04:16,912 --> 00:04:18,500
isn't worthy enough to stay beside you.

88
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:19,970
You're not welcome here.

89
00:04:20,580 --> 00:04:21,530
Hurry and scram!

90
00:04:21,940 --> 00:04:23,450
The chief and elders are speaking.

91
00:04:23,850 --> 00:04:24,890
How dare you interfere?

92
00:04:25,580 --> 00:04:27,140
Has Haotian Sect abandoned its rules?

93
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:29,890
As the sect's top disciple, Tang Hu

94
00:04:30,090 --> 00:04:32,330
was expressing our intentions
on our behalf.

95
00:04:32,530 --> 00:04:33,770
How is he wrong?

96
00:04:35,410 --> 00:04:36,060
Chief,

97
00:04:36,620 --> 00:04:38,330
hurry and kick him out

98
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:40,992
so that Haotian Sect
wouldn't be tainted by the likes of him.

99
00:04:42,330 --> 00:04:44,140
Elders, I understand your frustrations.

100
00:04:44,448 --> 00:04:46,180
I'm willing to atone
for my father's sin.

101
00:04:46,410 --> 00:04:48,450
Chief, elders, I only hope
that you guys can give me

102
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:50,700
a chance to return to my roots.

103
00:05:08,090 --> 00:05:08,770
I think

104
00:05:09,580 --> 00:05:11,970
this is enough to express
Tang Hao's sincerity, right?

105
00:05:12,820 --> 00:05:13,650
A soul bone?

106
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:15,700
This belongs to Tang Hao.

107
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:17,330
Is he dead?

108
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:18,090
No.

109
00:05:19,260 --> 00:05:20,650
He forcibly stripped this

110
00:05:20,940 --> 00:05:22,740
from himself alive.

111
00:05:24,380 --> 00:05:26,330
He's the son of the old chief after all.

112
00:05:27,330 --> 00:05:29,060
Seems like he always regretted

113
00:05:30,380 --> 00:05:31,890
what he did to the sect.

114
00:05:35,740 --> 00:05:38,090
These two soul bones
are the treasures of the sect.

115
00:05:38,890 --> 00:05:40,770
Now, the two elders can keep them.

116
00:05:41,740 --> 00:05:45,140
When you find the next sect successor

117
00:05:45,290 --> 00:05:47,850
or disciples who contribute
greatly to the sect,

118
00:05:48,380 --> 00:05:49,970
you may give them the soul bones.

119
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,424
Why would the old chief

120
00:05:57,850 --> 00:06:00,410
passed away suddenly

121
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:03,344
if Tang Hao didn't insist on
being together with a soul beast?

122
00:06:03,970 --> 00:06:06,890
Why would my sole son and
the young disciples of Haotian Sect

123
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:09,410
die fighting against Martial Soul Hall
had he not done so?

124
00:06:10,090 --> 00:06:11,500
Why would the mighty Haotian Sect

125
00:06:11,740 --> 00:06:14,464
become a reclusive sect had it
not because of his foolish actions?

126
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:17,530
Everything went downhill
because of what Tang Hao did.

127
00:06:17,650 --> 00:06:18,770
I'll never forgive him!

128
00:06:21,210 --> 00:06:23,450
Due to your father's actions,

129
00:06:24,140 --> 00:06:25,700
I won't let you return to the sect

130
00:06:25,744 --> 00:06:27,552
even if you've retrieved the soul bones.

131
00:06:27,850 --> 00:06:28,820
Moreover,

132
00:06:28,970 --> 00:06:30,580
he and that cursed soul beast

133
00:06:30,650 --> 00:06:31,580
gave birth to you!

134
00:06:43,380 --> 00:06:44,090
San,

135
00:06:44,090 --> 00:06:45,376
stop what you're doing right now!

136
00:06:54,260 --> 00:06:55,450
The Demon Domain, huh?

137
00:06:56,060 --> 00:06:57,410
You can criticize me all you like,

138
00:06:58,140 --> 00:06:59,940
but don't ever insult my mother.

139
00:07:00,530 --> 00:07:01,410
Seventh Elder,

140
00:07:01,820 --> 00:07:02,850
I challenge you to a duel.

141
00:07:03,328 --> 00:07:05,008
I might die, but I have no regrets.

142
00:07:07,140 --> 00:07:08,580
You wish to challenge me to a duel?

143
00:07:08,650 --> 00:07:09,290
That's right.

144
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:10,650
If you lose,

145
00:07:11,210 --> 00:07:12,700
you have to apologize to my mother.

146
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:17,970
This is preposterous.

147
00:07:18,090 --> 00:07:19,890
You think you have the right
to challenge me?

148
00:07:20,020 --> 00:07:21,700
Youngsters can be proud,

149
00:07:22,210 --> 00:07:23,890
but they shouldn't be arrogant.

150
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:24,800
You're young,

151
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:27,320
yet you intend to challenge
the elder of Haotian Sect to a duel?

152
00:07:27,328 --> 00:07:29,280
Are you belittling Haotian Sect now?

153
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:31,744
Elders, there's no need
to waste your breath on him.

154
00:07:31,890 --> 00:07:33,850
You can leave arrogant fools
like him to me.

155
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:35,580
I'll teach him a lesson.

156
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:38,380
Do I have the right to challenge you

157
00:07:39,180 --> 00:07:41,450
after defeating the top disciple,

158
00:07:41,450 --> 00:07:42,090
Seventh Elder?

159
00:07:42,450 --> 00:07:43,890
If you survive the duel,

160
00:07:44,530 --> 00:07:46,290
I'll accept your challenge.

161
00:07:51,020 --> 00:07:51,740
Okay.

162
00:08:05,020 --> 00:08:05,530
Tang Hu,

163
00:08:05,970 --> 00:08:07,850
Level 64 Storm Attack Branch
War Soul Emperor.

164
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:08,970
Please.

165
00:08:17,620 --> 00:08:18,290
Tang San,

166
00:08:18,890 --> 00:08:20,770
Level 59 Controlling Branch
War Soul King.

167
00:08:21,072 --> 00:08:22,960
How could the martial soul
of Haotian Hammer

168
00:08:23,090 --> 00:08:24,650
belong to a Controlling Soul Master?

169
00:08:30,090 --> 00:08:32,770
You'll find out later.

170
00:09:28,290 --> 00:09:29,410
Twin Martial Souls?

171
00:09:29,890 --> 00:09:30,650
That's right.

172
00:09:31,050 --> 00:09:33,340
It's the one-in-a-hundred
Twin Martial Souls.

173
00:09:35,570 --> 00:09:38,500
Twin Martial Souls
and the Demon Domain, huh?

174
00:09:39,340 --> 00:09:41,570
I suppose he has the right
to be arrogant.

175
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:01,980
Innate Domain?

176
00:10:03,340 --> 00:10:05,140
His mother, Yin,
left that behind for him.

177
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:30,740
You're powerful indeed.

178
00:10:35,740 --> 00:10:37,380
But I won't lose to you forever.

179
00:10:38,256 --> 00:10:39,776
We shall duel again in the future.

180
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,184
I shall wait for you.

181
00:10:44,620 --> 00:10:45,410
Seventh Elder,

182
00:10:45,890 --> 00:10:48,530
do I have the right
to challenge you now?

183
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:03,500
Help me put it on.

184
00:11:11,530 --> 00:11:12,170
Seventh Elder,

185
00:11:12,530 --> 00:11:13,024
this is...

186
00:11:13,472 --> 00:11:16,048
This is the only thing Senior
had left behind after his passing.

187
00:11:16,100 --> 00:11:16,810
Help me put it on.

188
00:11:17,340 --> 00:11:18,890
My son died with this equipped

189
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,770
while fighting against
the Martial Soul Hall.

190
00:11:21,050 --> 00:11:23,410
Today, I want him to see

191
00:11:24,140 --> 00:11:26,890
how I'm going to teach
Tang Hao's son a lesson.

192
00:11:27,500 --> 00:11:29,620
Since your father isn't back
to face his punishment,

193
00:11:30,140 --> 00:11:31,810
you shall face it on his behalf.

194
00:11:32,220 --> 00:11:33,340
If you lose,

195
00:11:34,170 --> 00:11:35,220
I hope you can take back

196
00:11:35,260 --> 00:11:36,460
your insults.

197
00:11:37,220 --> 00:11:38,740
And, I hope the elders can agree

198
00:11:40,460 --> 00:11:43,770
to give me a chance
to return to my roots.

199
00:11:58,500 --> 00:11:59,050
Father,

200
00:11:59,650 --> 00:12:01,140
this is my friend, Ma Hongjun.

201
00:12:01,220 --> 00:12:01,770
Hello.

202
00:12:02,736 --> 00:12:04,592
We infiltrated Xingluo City's
Martial Soul Hall

203
00:12:04,656 --> 00:12:06,960
in secret according to the leads
he provided us.

204
00:12:07,056 --> 00:12:09,200
However, it was already empty
when we reached there.

205
00:12:09,220 --> 00:12:09,690
The armors,

206
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:10,570
soul masters,

207
00:12:10,570 --> 00:12:12,460
even the Grand Chrysanthemum Master
was missing.

208
00:12:12,460 --> 00:12:13,620
I'm sure something's off.

209
00:12:13,980 --> 00:12:16,690
I'm worried that they might be
targeting Xingluo.

210
00:12:16,992 --> 00:12:19,296
Your Majesty, please investigate
the case thoroughly.

211
00:12:22,050 --> 00:12:24,690
Duke Lingmao investigated
the case long ago.

212
00:12:25,220 --> 00:12:26,220
I said this before.

213
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:28,400
You guys should only
focus on your cultivation.

214
00:12:28,770 --> 00:12:31,170
You guys shouldn't
meddle with state affairs.

215
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:32,050
Father,

216
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:34,170
I'm worried that this incident
might be related

217
00:12:34,380 --> 00:12:36,260
to the disappearance
of the soul masters.

218
00:12:36,336 --> 00:12:36,740
I wish...

219
00:12:36,740 --> 00:12:38,410
Just mind your own business!

220
00:12:40,410 --> 00:12:42,020
Even if they're up to no good,

221
00:12:42,650 --> 00:12:44,530
they're not targeting Xingluo.

222
00:12:45,220 --> 00:12:47,930
Now, all of the
Martial Soul Halls in Xingluo

223
00:12:47,980 --> 00:12:49,500
are empty.

224
00:12:50,020 --> 00:12:53,410
All of the soul masters
have left the city in secret.

225
00:12:55,620 --> 00:12:56,530
They left?

226
00:12:57,170 --> 00:12:57,890
Where did they go?

227
00:13:01,740 --> 00:13:02,770
Your Majesty,

228
00:13:02,860 --> 00:13:04,650
where did they go?

229
00:13:06,050 --> 00:13:06,770
Tiandou.

230
00:13:08,256 --> 00:13:10,240
Don't tell me
Martial Soul Hall is trying to...

231
00:13:10,256 --> 00:13:11,980
Their intention doesn't matter

232
00:13:12,380 --> 00:13:14,290
as long as they don't harm Xingluo.

233
00:13:14,860 --> 00:13:15,460
Father,

234
00:13:15,920 --> 00:13:17,360
we can't just stay out of this.

235
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,590
The survival of the two empires

236
00:13:18,608 --> 00:13:19,616
depends on each other.

237
00:13:19,648 --> 00:13:21,792
If Martial Soul Hall intends
to invade Tiandou,

238
00:13:21,808 --> 00:13:24,064
I'm afraid Xingluo won't be
able to escape unscathed.

239
00:13:24,096 --> 00:13:25,860
Depend on each other?

240
00:13:28,380 --> 00:13:30,050
We could profit from their conflict.

241
00:13:31,100 --> 00:13:33,100
You're still as dense as always.

242
00:13:34,530 --> 00:13:36,170
Although Martial Soul Hall is powerful,

243
00:13:36,220 --> 00:13:37,770
Tiandou isn't that weak.

244
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:39,952
We should reap the profit
after the conflict

245
00:13:40,016 --> 00:13:41,930
instead of joining it.

246
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:44,890
Your Majesty, aren't you worried...

247
00:13:44,890 --> 00:13:45,500
Enough!

248
00:13:47,260 --> 00:13:50,410
Zhuqing, although
you're a Six-Ring Soul Emperor now,

249
00:13:51,050 --> 00:13:52,020
don't forget

250
00:13:52,020 --> 00:13:54,220
that you two were the ones
who came up with the bet!

251
00:13:54,220 --> 00:13:56,190
Both parties must uphold
their end of the bargain!

252
00:13:58,170 --> 00:13:59,770
Do your part

253
00:14:00,170 --> 00:14:02,050
before you worry about other people.

254
00:14:03,170 --> 00:14:03,980
I understand.

255
00:14:04,592 --> 00:14:06,500
I'll improve my cultivation
as soon as possible.

256
00:14:07,380 --> 00:14:08,290
Remember,

257
00:14:09,008 --> 00:14:11,408
you don't even have the right
to negotiate a deal with me

258
00:14:11,530 --> 00:14:13,460
until you reach the required level,

259
00:14:13,930 --> 00:14:16,290
not to mention saving
Dai Weisi and Zhu Zhuyun.

260
00:14:17,410 --> 00:14:18,050
Leave.

261
00:14:20,810 --> 00:14:21,890
I shall take my leave.

262
00:14:25,100 --> 00:14:25,980
I shall take my leave.

263
00:14:28,650 --> 00:14:29,570
I shall take my leave.

264
00:14:33,520 --> 00:14:35,952
Make sure our men keep an eye
on Mubai and Zhuqing.

265
00:14:35,980 --> 00:14:37,664
Do not let them leave the palace again.

266
00:14:38,384 --> 00:14:39,312
Yes, Your Majesty.

267
00:14:40,260 --> 00:14:41,980
Now, I finally understand.

268
00:14:42,100 --> 00:14:43,530
Crown Prince? Crown Princess?

269
00:14:43,552 --> 00:14:46,080
None of you can lead a life
as carefree as a commoner like me.

270
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:47,380
