377
00:20:53,810 --> 00:20:54,220
San,

378
00:20:54,336 --> 00:20:55,264
how are you feeling?

379
00:20:55,660 --> 00:20:56,180
First Uncle,

380
00:20:56,530 --> 00:20:57,090
