410
00:22:09,020 --> 00:22:09,700
Seven,

411
00:22:09,792 --> 00:22:11,328
in the end, you used all of your power.

412
00:22:11,500 --> 00:22:12,980
You lost the duel.

413
00:22:13,700 --> 00:22:16,290
And, the kid gave up on attacking you
because he wanted

414
00:22:16,570 --> 00:22:17,810
to protect the shoulder guard.

415
00:22:18,180 --> 00:22:20,500
He had no choice but to take on
the full blow.

416
00:22:30,180 --> 00:22:31,090
