417
00:22:35,020 --> 00:22:35,700
Seven,

418
00:22:36,770 --> 00:22:37,810
head back and rest.

419
00:22:38,220 --> 00:22:38,570
No.

420
00:22:39,290 --> 00:22:40,220
I can't just leave.

421
00:22:40,980 --> 00:22:42,090
I'm not a sore loser.

422
00:22:42,220 --> 00:22:43,330
Since I've lost,

423
00:22:44,180 --> 00:22:46,290
I have to fulfill my promise.

424
00:22:47,940 --> 00:22:50,570
I'll wait here until
he regains consciousness.

425
00:22:52,370 --> 00:22:53,020
Yuehua,

426
00:22:53,530 --> 00:22:56,530
you can start preparing for
the ancestral recognition ceremony.

427
00:22:57,328 --> 00:22:59,296
Elders, thank you for
fulfilling his wish.

428
00:23:04,610 --> 00:23:06,330
He fulfilled his own wish.

429
00:23:06,660 --> 00:23:07,500
I've never seen

430
00:23:07,500 --> 00:23:09,330
a young man as outstanding as him.

431
00:23:11,940 --> 00:23:13,130
Maybe he's the person

432
00:23:13,610 --> 00:23:15,940
that Haotian Sect
has been waiting for all along.

433
00:23:18,420 --> 00:23:21,090
I just hope that he won't
take the wrong path

434
00:23:22,420 --> 00:23:23,940
and repeat his father's mistake.

435
00:23:31,740 --> 00:23:33,460
The situation is worse than I thought.

436
00:23:33,900 --> 00:23:35,370
The peripheral area of Xingdou Forest

437
00:23:35,424 --> 00:23:38,064
has too many high-level soul beasts
from the mixed zone.

438
00:23:38,610 --> 00:23:40,260
The soul beasts are killing each other.

439
00:23:40,810 --> 00:23:43,460
Xingdou Forest is in complete chaos now.

440
00:23:52,700 --> 00:23:53,810
Xingdou Forest

441
00:23:53,900 --> 00:23:55,770
was greatly affected this time.

442
00:23:56,128 --> 00:23:58,576
I assume it'll take a long time
before the forest can recover.

443
00:24:00,090 --> 00:24:01,530
If only Tang San

444
00:24:01,530 --> 00:24:02,260
were around.

445
00:24:03,130 --> 00:24:04,740
This concerns Xingdou Forest.

446
00:24:05,090 --> 00:24:06,560
What has this got to do with him?

447
00:24:06,660 --> 00:24:09,660
Previously, he always supported
Wu with his power from a distance.

448
00:24:09,850 --> 00:24:11,290
This time, maybe he can come up

449
00:24:11,460 --> 00:24:13,460
with a method to heal the forest.

450
00:24:14,940 --> 00:24:16,090
Method to heal the forest?

451
00:24:17,130 --> 00:24:17,850
I got it!

452
00:24:18,220 --> 00:24:18,610
Erming,

453
00:24:18,740 --> 00:24:19,220
thank you!

454
00:24:20,940 --> 00:24:21,740
You're thanking me?

455
00:24:22,800 --> 00:24:24,608
It's about the method
to heal the forest.

456
00:24:24,740 --> 00:24:26,530
We have to align with the natural order.

457
00:24:27,610 --> 00:24:29,740
We have to use the forest's power
to heal the forest.

458
00:24:30,370 --> 00:24:31,220
Wu,

459
00:24:31,420 --> 00:24:32,810
what does that mean?

460
00:24:33,330 --> 00:24:36,050
Are you saying that we can
stay out of this?

461
00:24:36,420 --> 00:24:37,040
That's not it.

462
00:24:37,104 --> 00:24:38,660
You guys have to help the forest out.

463
00:24:38,704 --> 00:24:40,576
It's because you guys
are the forest's power.

464
00:24:40,810 --> 00:24:41,740
Us?

465
00:24:44,020 --> 00:24:44,530
Erming,

466
00:24:44,592 --> 00:24:45,220
come with me.

467
00:24:45,264 --> 00:24:46,704
Let's head to the peripheral area.

468
00:24:56,260 --> 00:24:56,900
(Wu,)

469
00:24:57,180 --> 00:24:58,180
(what should we do?)

470
00:24:58,832 --> 00:25:01,792
(The law of nature teaches the
soul beasts to avoid natural predators.)

471
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:03,550
(They need to seek benefits
and avoid harm.)

472
00:25:03,580 --> 00:25:05,499
(To the soul beasts in Xingdou Forest,)

473
00:25:05,500 --> 00:25:07,250
(you guys, who have
lived for 10,000 years)

474
00:25:07,280 --> 00:25:08,784
(are the leaders of the forest.)

475
00:25:08,816 --> 00:25:10,256
(None of them can disobey you two.)

476
00:25:10,448 --> 00:25:11,980
(Therefore, you guys are the only ones)

477
00:25:11,980 --> 00:25:14,830
(that can herd the soul beasts that have
gathered in the peripheral area)

478
00:25:14,848 --> 00:25:16,010
(back to where they belong.)

479
00:25:50,660 --> 00:25:52,570
(All of us are part of
the forest's power.)

480
00:25:53,220 --> 00:25:55,050
(When nature loses its balance,)

481
00:25:55,500 --> 00:25:57,130
(we should do what we're supposed to do)

482
00:25:57,290 --> 00:25:58,500
(and use our power)

483
00:25:58,640 --> 00:26:00,304
(to help everything get back on track.)

484
00:26:30,810 --> 00:26:33,020
I heard that there's an animal

485
00:26:33,050 --> 00:26:34,980
called a shepherd dog
in the human world.

486
00:26:35,420 --> 00:26:37,220
Does it resemble us?

487
00:26:37,808 --> 00:26:40,016
