a shepherd ape?

488
00:26:47,264 --> 00:26:49,180
Haotian Sect has gone
into hiding for 20 years.

489
00:26:49,600 --> 00:26:50,570
Isn't it time for us

490
00:26:50,850 --> 00:26:51,700
to return

491
00:26:51,700 --> 00:26:53,180
to the Soul Master's world?

492
00:26:54,130 --> 00:26:56,090
Our sect has mentioned this many times.

493
00:26:56,810 --> 00:27:00,050
I suppose the time is ripe.

494
00:27:00,290 --> 00:27:00,700
No.

495
00:27:01,900 --> 00:27:02,940
