498
00:27:11,900 --> 00:27:12,980
Now, it seems like

499
00:27:13,530 --> 00:27:15,940
we have to lay low for a little longer.

500
00:27:19,180 --> 00:27:20,090
Is it because

501
00:27:21,370 --> 00:27:22,020
of San?

502
00:27:22,420 --> 00:27:23,810
Haotian Sect needs

503
00:27:24,570 --> 00:27:27,180
a leader capable of guiding the sect

504
00:27:27,330 --> 00:27:29,330
towards innovation and progress.

505
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:30,770
All of us are old now.

506
00:27:31,090 --> 00:27:32,260
You're getting older too.

507
00:27:33,020 --> 00:27:34,420
But the kid is different.

508
00:27:34,770 --> 00:27:36,700
He's exceptionally talented.

509
00:27:37,020 --> 00:27:38,740
We can't afford to neglect him.

510
00:27:39,500 --> 00:27:41,570
What he needs are
experience and cultivation.

511
00:27:42,420 --> 00:27:43,130
Second Uncle,

512
00:27:44,460 --> 00:27:46,370
