513
00:27:49,050 --> 00:27:51,330
The past cannot be changed.

514
00:27:52,220 --> 00:27:53,660
For the future of our sect,

515
00:27:55,090 --> 00:27:56,980
I still require Tang San to prove

516
00:27:57,500 --> 00:27:59,940
that he's determined enough
to carry this responsibility.

517
00:28:27,090 --> 00:28:28,530
You forced me to use my full power,

518
00:28:29,660 --> 00:28:31,168
