519
00:28:31,290 --> 00:28:32,180
Kid,

520
00:28:32,900 --> 00:28:34,330
you're pretty capable.

521
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:36,816
Seventh Elder,
thank you for your praise.

522
00:28:36,850 --> 00:28:38,980
