527
00:28:58,980 --> 00:29:00,020
I won't

528
00:29:00,370 --> 00:29:01,130
express my thanks.

529
00:29:01,728 --> 00:29:02,980
I will fulfill my promise.

530
00:29:05,770 --> 00:29:06,290
