to your mother officially.

532
00:29:09,700 --> 00:29:11,220
Although she's a soul beast,

533
00:29:11,290 --> 00:29:13,770
the Haotian Sect isn't
a narrow-minded organization.

534
00:29:13,900 --> 00:29:14,980
We aren't inherently biased.

535
00:29:15,536 --> 00:29:17,460
It's just that we lost control
of the situation

536
00:29:17,610 --> 00:29:18,570
gradually.

537
00:29:20,016 --> 00:29:21,940
That's why an old
and stubborn man like me

538
00:29:21,984 --> 00:29:23,504
is venting my frustrations on her.

539
00:29:25,420 --> 00:29:25,900
Tang San,

540
00:29:27,290 --> 00:29:28,850
I agree to let you return to your roots.

541
00:29:29,090 --> 00:29:32,180
Now, you're an official member
of Haotian Sect.

542
00:29:34,512 --> 00:29:35,680
You may go inside.

543
00:29:35,980 --> 00:29:38,130
Chief and Second Elder
are waiting for you inside.

544
00:30:18,460 --> 00:30:19,130
Thank you, Chief

545
00:30:19,328 --> 00:30:20,288
