547
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:23,600
and fulfill my father's wish.

548
00:30:25,290 --> 00:30:27,370
May I pay respect to Grandfather now?

549
00:30:27,850 --> 00:30:30,020
The sect was in huge trouble
because of your father.

550
00:30:31,330 --> 00:30:33,700
The old chief couldn't forgive him

551
00:30:33,740 --> 00:30:35,312
even before he took his last breath.

552
00:30:35,530 --> 00:30:37,740
Although we allowed you
to return to your roots,

553
00:30:38,260 --> 00:30:40,850
the old chief always hoped

554
00:30:41,530 --> 00:30:43,660
that Haotian Sect could produce

555
00:30:43,980 --> 00:30:46,090
an exceptionally talented young disciple

556
00:30:46,500 --> 00:30:48,980
that could help the sect
regain its former glory.

557
00:30:49,500 --> 00:30:51,570
If you can complete three tasks for us,

558
00:30:51,840 --> 00:30:53,980
not only will you be able
to return to your roots,

559
00:30:54,370 --> 00:30:56,020
but we can also allow your father

560
00:30:56,460 --> 00:30:58,180
to return to the sect

561
00:30:58,420 --> 00:31:00,810
so that you two could pay respect
to the old chief together.

562
00:31:02,960 --> 00:31:03,610
All right.

563
00:31:04,180 --> 00:31:04,740
I promise you.

564
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:07,024
These three tasks are
extraordinarily difficult.

565
00:31:07,220 --> 00:31:08,330
According to what I know,

566
00:31:08,770 --> 00:31:09,740
no one in the history

567
00:31:09,740 --> 00:31:11,632
of Douluo Continent
had ever completed them.

568
00:31:11,940 --> 00:31:14,740
Even so, are you sure
you want to take up the tasks?

569
00:31:15,130 --> 00:31:16,768
No matter what kind of tasks they are,

570
00:31:17,152 --> 00:31:18,090
I will complete them.

571
00:31:18,144 --> 00:31:20,130
It's because this is a promise
I made to Father.

572
00:31:20,608 --> 00:31:22,416
It's also a promise I made to the sect.

573
00:31:22,850 --> 00:31:23,850
For the first task,

574
00:31:24,810 --> 00:31:26,570
your soul power needs to exceed Level 80

575
00:31:27,090 --> 00:31:29,050
within ten years.

576
00:31:29,290 --> 00:31:31,260
I believe I can achieve that.

577
00:31:31,660 --> 00:31:32,570
For the second task,

578
00:31:32,976 --> 00:31:34,130
defeat a Grand Soul Master

579
00:31:34,180 --> 00:31:36,940
of Martial Soul Hall within ten years.

580
00:31:43,370 --> 00:31:44,500
For the third task,

581
00:31:45,090 --> 00:31:47,260
when your soul power reaches Level 80,

582
00:31:47,570 --> 00:31:50,220
you need to obtain
a Hectomillennium Soul Ring.

583
00:31:54,090 --> 00:31:54,900
Second Elder,

584
00:31:55,420 --> 00:31:56,180
even most

585
00:31:56,290 --> 00:31:58,460
of the Grand Soul Masters
couldn't complete that task.

586
00:31:58,496 --> 00:32:01,152
Ordinary soul masters will never
be able to complete the task.

587
00:32:01,184 --> 00:32:03,290
However, the future leader
of Haotian Sect

588
00:32:05,530 --> 00:32:06,570
has to complete it.

589
00:32:07,760 --> 00:32:09,500
Although these
three tasks are difficult,

590
00:32:09,610 --> 00:32:11,370
they represent our expectations of you.

591
00:32:11,900 --> 00:32:13,660
If you can complete them in time,

592
00:32:16,090 --> 00:32:18,180
you shall be the next sect leader.

593
00:32:20,500 --> 00:32:22,180
By then, no one will stop you

594
00:32:22,570 --> 00:32:24,420
no matter what you want to do.

595
00:32:25,370 --> 00:32:25,980
I

596
00:32:27,090 --> 00:32:28,020
will complete them.

597
00:32:50,020 --> 00:32:50,500
(Father,)

598
00:32:51,770 --> 00:32:53,020
(although these three tasks)

599
00:32:53,460 --> 00:32:55,420
(are extremely difficult,)

600
00:32:56,330 --> 00:32:57,700
(I'll fulfill my promise.)

601
00:32:58,090 --> 00:33:00,290
(I won't let you or the sect down.)

602
00:33:01,050 --> 00:33:02,130
(Given enough time,)

603
00:33:02,610 --> 00:33:03,740
(I'll surely return here)

604
00:33:04,290 --> 00:33:07,260
(and restore Haotian Sect
to its former glory.)

605
00:33:29,810 --> 00:33:30,740
(San,)

606
00:33:31,740 --> 00:33:34,810
(I'll leave Haotian Sect to you.)

607
00:33:37,660 --> 00:33:38,500
(I believe)

608
00:33:39,330 --> 00:33:42,570
(that you can surely achieve
what I couldn't back then.)

609
00:33:55,900 --> 00:33:57,290
Judging from His Majesty's pulse,

610
00:33:57,770 --> 00:34:00,610
I think someone
has swapped his medicine.

611
00:34:00,810 --> 00:34:03,420
Father's meals and prescriptions

612
00:34:03,770 --> 00:34:05,660
have to undergo a strict inspection.

613
00:34:06,020 --> 00:34:08,170
There's no way an outsider
can tamper with them.

614
00:34:08,380 --> 00:34:09,460
Unless it's...

615
00:34:10,050 --> 00:34:10,780
Reporting in!

616
00:34:12,096 --> 00:34:12,730
Your Highness,

617
00:34:12,736 --> 00:34:14,440
you told us to set up
an ambush in the dark

618
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,609
and subdue suspicious persons.

619
00:34:15,610 --> 00:34:16,570
Someone fell for our trap!

620
00:34:16,576 --> 00:34:17,136
Who is it?

621
00:34:17,210 --> 00:34:17,940
Where is he?

622
00:34:18,380 --> 00:34:19,500
Such audacity!

623
00:34:19,730 --> 00:34:21,200
How dare you guys do this to me?

624
00:34:21,730 --> 00:34:22,090
Brother,

625
00:34:22,530 --> 00:34:23,460
tell them to release me!

626
00:34:25,380 --> 00:34:26,224
Put down your spears.

627
00:34:27,730 --> 00:34:29,552
So, you swapped out
Father's medicine, huh?

628
00:34:29,860 --> 00:34:31,250
Are you trying to harm Father here?

629
00:34:31,312 --> 00:34:32,560
What are you talking about?

630
00:34:32,610 --> 00:34:33,700
Who's trying to harm Father?

631
00:34:33,730 --> 00:34:35,248
I should be asking you that question.

632
00:34:35,500 --> 00:34:37,170
Why did you sneak to Father's chamber?

633
00:34:38,090 --> 00:34:39,728
You didn't allow anyone to visit Father.

634
00:34:39,824 --> 00:34:41,170
I had no choice but to sneak in.

635
00:34:42,020 --> 00:34:42,980
Brother, do you think

636
00:34:43,020 --> 00:34:44,480
only you're concerned about Father?

637
00:34:44,530 --> 00:34:45,312
Search his body.

638
00:34:46,780 --> 00:34:47,420
How dare you?

639
00:34:48,380 --> 00:34:49,690
I'm one of the princes!

640
00:34:49,728 --> 00:34:51,680
I won't let you guys
disrespect me like this!

641
00:34:52,570 --> 00:34:53,340
Xue Qinghe,

642
00:34:54,090 --> 00:34:55,170
once Father has recovered,

643
00:34:55,250 --> 00:34:57,050
I'll surely ask him
to uphold justice for me!

644
00:34:57,050 --> 00:34:57,690
Fourth Brother,

645
00:34:57,888 --> 00:34:59,380
someone swapped Father's medicine.

646
00:34:59,500 --> 00:35:01,020
This concerns his safety.

647
00:35:01,090 --> 00:35:02,416
I can't afford to take the risk.

648
00:35:04,896 --> 00:35:05,650
Search his body.

649
00:35:05,900 --> 00:35:07,280
This has nothing to do with me!

650
00:35:07,530 --> 00:35:08,650
I'm the fourth prince!

651
00:35:08,980 --> 00:35:09,820
By doing this to me,

652
00:35:09,980 --> 00:35:11,530
you guys are insulting the royal family!

653
00:35:22,460 --> 00:35:23,610
You'll regret this.

654
00:35:31,568 --> 00:35:32,650
Continue the search.

655
00:35:35,170 --> 00:35:36,380
You may choose to doubt me.

656
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:38,860
However, you have to show evidence.

657
00:35:40,050 --> 00:35:40,980
On the contrary,

658
00:35:41,530 --> 00:35:43,020
if something happens to Father,

659
00:35:43,900 --> 00:35:46,090
shouldn't you be
the main suspect instead?

660
00:35:50,980 --> 00:35:51,530
Your Highness,

661
00:35:51,530 --> 00:35:52,848
someone wishes to see His Majesty.

662
00:35:52,896 --> 00:35:54,016
He's waiting at the entrance.

663
00:35:58,650 --> 00:35:59,650
Xue Qinghe.

664
00:36:01,460 --> 00:36:02,610
I'll remember

665
00:36:03,980 --> 00:36:05,050
what you did to me today.

666
00:36:05,170 --> 00:36:06,780
I know that was a tough pill to swallow.

667
00:36:07,456 --> 00:36:09,360
But I hope that you can understand this.

668
00:36:10,020 --> 00:36:12,210
I can't afford to let anything
happen to Father.

669
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:13,860
I have no choice.

670
00:37:06,460 --> 00:37:07,020
Grandmaster.

671
00:37:07,570 --> 00:37:08,130
Master.

672
00:37:09,610 --> 00:37:10,460
Your Highness,

673
00:37:10,650 --> 00:37:11,984
please tell the guards to leave.

674
00:37:12,020 --> 00:37:13,840
We have something
to report to His Majesty.

675
00:37:15,050 --> 00:37:18,980
Someone secretly swapped
Father's medicine a few days ago.

676
00:37:19,610 --> 00:37:21,020
We're still investigating the case.

677
00:37:21,090 --> 00:37:22,610
This concerns his safety.

678
00:37:22,650 --> 00:37:25,090
Therefore, I'm afraid
I cannot let you two see His Majesty

679
00:37:25,210 --> 00:37:27,210
before we reach a conclusion.

680
00:37:27,420 --> 00:37:28,250
Please forgive me.

681
00:37:28,690 --> 00:37:29,860
That actually happened?

682
00:37:30,640 --> 00:37:32,130
If so, how's His Majesty doing now?

683
00:37:32,380 --> 00:37:33,250
He's currently fine.

684
00:37:33,300 --> 00:37:34,768
He just needs to rest and recuperate.

685
00:37:35,232 --> 00:37:38,128
Could it be that members of Martial
Soul Hall have infiltrated the palace?

686
00:37:39,530 --> 00:37:40,980
We cannot determine

687
00:37:41,050 --> 00:37:42,250
the culprit as of yet.

688
00:37:42,688 --> 00:37:45,090
What urgent matter do you guys
have to report to His Majesty?

689
00:37:45,420 --> 00:37:47,232
Why don't you guys
discuss it with me first?

690
00:37:47,264 --> 00:37:48,656
We can make a decision together.

691
00:37:57,024 --> 00:37:59,650
Martial Soul Hall has recruited an army
of soul masters in Xingluo.

692
00:37:59,730 --> 00:38:00,864
They're heading to Tiandou?

693
00:38:01,820 --> 00:38:02,420
Grandmaster,

694
00:38:02,464 --> 00:38:03,940
where did you receive this news from?

695
00:38:03,950 --> 00:38:05,120
Is the news source reliable?

696
00:38:05,120 --> 00:38:07,610
It was discovered by one of my students,
who was traveling abroad.

697
00:38:07,610 --> 00:38:08,250
It's reliable.

698
00:38:09,650 --> 00:38:10,250
Your Highness,

699
00:38:10,610 --> 00:38:13,179
Martial Soul Hall had been
recruiting soul masters before this.

700
00:38:13,180 --> 00:38:14,810
Now, the number
of soul masters they have

701
00:38:14,816 --> 00:38:15,940
is almost equal to Tiandou.

702
00:38:16,112 --> 00:38:17,610
And now, they're gathering in secret.

703
00:38:17,650 --> 00:38:18,672
Their motives are unknown.

704
00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:20,896
I'm afraid they're trying
to stage a rebellion.

705
00:38:21,130 --> 00:38:23,380
Martial Soul Hall's behavior
is questionable indeed.

706
00:38:23,900 --> 00:38:25,530
However, we don't have
concrete evidence.

707
00:38:25,690 --> 00:38:27,050
We cannot question them in public.

708
00:38:27,472 --> 00:38:30,224
I'll send my men to investigate the case
and gather evidence now.

709
00:38:30,256 --> 00:38:32,900
This time, Tiandou
can't afford to spare them again.

710
00:38:33,610 --> 00:38:35,820
I'm afraid we have to form
a defense plan.

711
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:37,072
I'll station my troops here

712
00:38:37,088 --> 00:38:38,249
to guard the palace entrance

713
00:38:38,250 --> 00:38:39,056
and the city pass.

714
00:38:39,072 --> 00:38:39,792
Grandmaster.

715
00:38:39,808 --> 00:38:42,200
You're the Chief of Soul Master
appointed by Father himself.

716
00:38:42,210 --> 00:38:44,130
I need you to deploy
the soul masters under you

717
00:38:44,460 --> 00:38:45,300
to defend the palace.

718
00:38:46,020 --> 00:38:47,300
I will not let you down.

719
00:38:48,020 --> 00:38:50,530
I'll also deploy the elite soul masters
of the Qibao Amber Sect

720
00:38:50,560 --> 00:38:52,272
to assist Grandmaster
with his arrangement

721
00:38:52,288 --> 00:38:54,112
so that His Majesty may remain safe.

722
00:38:54,112 --> 00:38:55,300
Master, thank you.

723
00:38:55,500 --> 00:38:56,170
Your Highness,

724
00:38:56,256 --> 00:38:57,344
we have no time to waste.

725
00:38:57,360 --> 00:38:59,408
Chief Ning and I will make
arrangements for it now.

726
00:39:16,048 --> 00:39:17,380
(Grand Porcupinefish Master)

727
00:39:17,380 --> 00:39:18,570
Tell Martial Soul Hall

728
00:39:18,730 --> 00:39:19,980
to act quickly

729
00:39:20,460 --> 00:39:22,020
to avoid unnecessary trouble.

730
00:39:22,816 --> 00:39:23,600
Yes, Your Highness.

731
00:39:31,420 --> 00:39:31,980
Your Highness!

732
00:39:33,980 --> 00:39:34,780
What happened?

733
00:39:40,980 --> 00:39:42,570
Did you take His Majesty's medicine?

734
00:39:43,570 --> 00:39:44,690
He was suspicious of me.

735
00:39:45,130 --> 00:39:46,570
Luckily, he didn't find the medicine.

736
00:39:47,340 --> 00:39:49,500
This isn't the time
to go against him in public.

737
00:39:49,552 --> 00:39:51,040
However, judging from his reaction,

738
00:39:51,210 --> 00:39:53,020
I'm sure that he's behind everything.

739
00:39:53,650 --> 00:39:55,210
He's afraid that we might foil his plan.

740
00:39:56,090 --> 00:39:56,380
You...

741
00:39:56,500 --> 00:39:56,820
No...

742
00:40:32,170 --> 00:40:34,500
We've already alerted him
to our presence.

743
00:40:35,380 --> 00:40:37,940
It won't be as simple
if we try to help His Majesty

744
00:40:38,500 --> 00:40:40,050
suppress the toxin in his body again.

745
00:40:40,416 --> 00:40:41,780
How's the research on the antidote?

746
00:40:42,250 --> 00:40:44,460
The toxin in His Majesty's body
is extremely complex.

747
00:40:45,250 --> 00:40:47,420
It's much harder to create the antidote
than I imagine.

748
00:40:48,130 --> 00:40:51,820
I'm worried that he can't last
until the antidote is completed.

749
00:40:52,300 --> 00:40:53,380
Since that's the case,

750
00:40:53,860 --> 00:40:56,610
taking a risk is our only option.

751
00:41:12,690 --> 00:41:15,300
Now that both of you
have reached Level 60,

752
00:41:15,730 --> 00:41:17,020
I'll fulfill my promise.

753
00:41:17,380 --> 00:41:18,530
I'll spare them from death.

754
00:41:20,860 --> 00:41:22,320
Strip them of their martial souls.

755
00:41:24,460 --> 00:41:24,860
Father!

756
00:41:25,780 --> 00:41:26,300
Your Majesty,

757
00:41:26,336 --> 00:41:29,136
please allow Zhu Zhuyun and Dai Weisi
to retain their martial souls.

758
00:41:29,900 --> 00:41:32,500
Why can't you guys understand?

759
00:41:32,816 --> 00:41:35,820
Killing them or stripping them of
their martial souls was never the goal.

760
00:41:36,420 --> 00:41:38,900
Consolidating royal power
is the core of the ancestral system.

761
00:41:39,860 --> 00:41:43,120
This is what the royal family of Xingluo
had done since thousands of years ago.

762
00:41:44,570 --> 00:41:45,940
You guys are still young.

763
00:41:46,690 --> 00:41:49,170
You guys underestimate
the human desire for power.

764
00:41:50,050 --> 00:41:51,420
Compared to power,

765
00:41:52,780 --> 00:41:54,860
we desire to choose
our own path in life.

766
00:41:54,980 --> 00:41:55,460
Father,

767
00:41:56,300 --> 00:41:58,250
I know that Xingluo
established such a system

768
00:41:58,940 --> 00:42:00,820
due to the internal
power struggle in the past.

769
00:42:01,170 --> 00:42:01,980
But in reality,

770
00:42:02,384 --> 00:42:04,976
brothers might not turn against
each other because of power.

771
00:42:04,992 --> 00:42:07,008
It's more likely
that they'll help each other out.

772
00:42:07,460 --> 00:42:08,050
Enough!

773
00:42:09,570 --> 00:42:11,610
I've already made repeated concessions

774
00:42:11,780 --> 00:42:12,900
because of your persistence.

775
00:42:13,300 --> 00:42:16,300
But the bottom line of Xingluo Empire
cannot be compromised.

776
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:19,088
You guys are powerful candidates
selected by our ancestral system.

777
00:42:19,120 --> 00:42:20,880
You guys have to accept your fate!

778
00:42:29,170 --> 00:42:29,780
Such audacity!

779
00:42:30,820 --> 00:42:31,300
Fatty!

780
00:42:31,380 --> 00:42:31,820
Don't move.

781
00:42:36,130 --> 00:42:36,650
Your Majesty,

782
00:42:36,768 --> 00:42:38,860
won't the royal family of Xingluo
worry about this?

783
00:42:38,980 --> 00:42:41,130
If the prince dies now,

784
00:42:41,380 --> 00:42:43,650
who will inherit Xingluo Empire?

785
00:42:43,860 --> 00:42:44,820
Release him.

786
00:42:44,940 --> 00:42:47,152
Your Majesty, I just wish
to give you a reminder.

787
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:48,699
Your ancestral system only serves to

788
00:42:48,700 --> 00:42:51,008
keep him alive because your
ancestors think other princes

789
00:42:51,020 --> 00:42:52,530
will harm him.

790
00:42:53,050 --> 00:42:55,690
If so, can your ancestral system
guarantee

791
00:42:55,760 --> 00:42:57,872
that other people will not harm
the crown prince?

792
00:42:58,170 --> 00:42:59,280
If they do get their way,

793
00:42:59,488 --> 00:43:02,064
don't you think the royal family
of Xingluo is in huge trouble?

794
00:43:02,170 --> 00:43:03,210
You're overthinking it.

795
00:43:07,900 --> 00:43:08,340
Fatty!

796
00:43:08,380 --> 00:43:08,690
Fatty!

797
00:43:32,473 --> 00:43:34,623
♪Ending the despair of suffering♪

798
00:43:34,623 --> 00:43:36,633
♪Justice runs deep in our veins♪

799
00:43:36,633 --> 00:43:38,183
♪The humble but powerful♪

800
00:43:38,183 --> 00:43:40,703
♪Will break open the world of darkness♪

801
00:43:40,703 --> 00:43:42,743
♪Engraving the words of good and evil♪

802
00:43:42,743 --> 00:43:44,753
♪Into the pages of history♪

803
00:43:44,753 --> 00:43:46,533
♪The remains of courage
on the shoulders♪

804
00:43:46,533 --> 00:43:48,523
♪Still shine with light♪

805
00:43:48,523 --> 00:43:50,103
♪Burn♪

806
00:43:50,563 --> 00:43:55,353
♪The hidden and mysterious soul♪

807
00:43:55,913 --> 00:43:57,923
♪Take on the future♪

808
00:43:57,923 --> 00:43:59,893
♪And triumph over fate♪

809
00:44:00,023 --> 00:44:03,973
♪Together, we forge a new era♪

810
00:44:03,973 --> 00:44:05,983
♪Yet be brave to fight on♪

811
00:44:05,983 --> 00:44:08,133
♪As a hero♪

812
00:44:08,133 --> 00:44:10,153
♪Protecting the light of justice♪

813
00:44:10,153 --> 00:44:13,263
♪With unwavering resolve,
marching forward without fear♪

814
00:44:15,253 --> 00:44:17,273
♪Consumed and engulfed by fate♪

815
00:44:17,273 --> 00:44:19,293
♪The flame within burns
